{"tid":495010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又話豁免廢老？90歲老伯入住護老院，房署指濫用公屋，要求遷出","createTime":"2017-12-10T09:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T09:25:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6804d9f65dcd2dd10d91f0232c1258ef82a25201","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"現年90歲的劉麟瑞老伯，在彩虹邨一個公屋單位居住超過半個世紀，三年前因病患入住護老院，結果被房署指濫用公屋，要求他遷出。不過，劉伯其實打算居家安老，他兩年多前患上大腸癌，在公立醫院做手術，此後接受特殊護理，故被其子女安排入住一間提供24小時病患託管護理及康復照顧的私營護老院。兩年多以來，他的情況已逐步好轉，醫生今年6月指，他目前能夠自行如廁，可以在家人的照顧下回家療養。<br />\n<br />\n1963年11月：劉家搬入彩虹邨公屋單位<br />\n<br />\n2008年7月7日：資助房屋小組委員會通過政策，若發現租戶逾三個月「非經常持續居於單位」，房委會便會採取「終止租約行動」<br />\n<br />\n2009年10月：原戶主劉太逝世<br />\n<br />\n2010年2月：劉伯與房委會重新簽署租約，成為單位戶主<br />\n<br />\n2014年10月：劉伯患上大腸癌，在公立醫院做手術後入住護老院<br />\n<br />\n2016年5月13日：房署向醫管局發信，要求醫管局提供劉伯最新登記地址<br />\n<br />\n2016年6月1日：醫管局向房署提供劉伯最新登記地址<br />\n<br />\n2016年6月13日：房署向入境處發信，要求入境處提供劉伯過去3年的出入境紀錄<br />\n<br />\n2016年6月22日：入境處向房署提供劉伯過去3年的出入境紀錄；根據房署的《調查報告》，屋邨辦事處同日從善用公屋資源分組接收到劉伯的案件<br />\n<br />\n2016年7月7日至2017年2月13日：房署進行14次家訪，未有遇見劉伯<br />\n<br />\n2017年2月16日：房署人員到私營護老院調查<br />\n<br />\n2017年3月22日：劉伯收到房署信件，指他沒有經常持續居住其公屋單位，要求他4月3日攜同該信到彩虹邨辦事處<br />\n<br />\n2017年3月24日：劉伯兒子去信房委會，解釋劉伯因病患傷殘在護老院接受照顧<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月3日：劉伯女兒到彩虹邨辦事處與辦事處職員會面，對方口頭指會於4月發「遷出通知書」，又指沒有經常持續居住所指的是「三個月」<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月6 日至2017年4月27 日：劉伯向房署申請女兒「有條件暫准居住」、劉伯兒子3次去信房委會<br />\n<br />\n2017年5月4日：劉伯在家人陪同下到彩虹邨辦事處交租，並向職員展示病患情況<br />\n<br />\n2017年5月10日：劉伯兒子再去信房委會；劉家向房署查詢「有條件暫准居住」申請進度<br />\n<br />\n2017年5月31日：房署向劉伯發出「遷出通知書」<br />\n<br />\n2017年6月1日：房署拒絕「有條件暫准居住」申請<br />\n<br />\n2017年6月3日：泌尿專科醫生診斷證明，劉伯健康狀況良好，能夠自行如廁，可以在家人的照顧下回家療養<br />\n<br />\n2017年6月14日：劉家提交上訴書<br />\n<br />\n2017年8月31日：護老院發信澄清<br />\n<br />\n2017年9月11日：上訴聆訊<br />\n<br />\n2017年9月19日：上訴委員會通知劉伯上訴聆訊的結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/8095/濫用公屋-房屋署-私隱專員公署-8129/查濫用公屋-家屬質疑房署違程序公義-眾新聞揭三大問題\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F8095%2F%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B-%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E7%BD%B2-%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2-8129%2F%E6%9F%A5%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%88%BF%E7%BD%B2%E9%81%95%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9-%E7%9C%BE%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%8F%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C&d=0SiDj62cuN3EJFKh3J%2F8Khv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=67167776\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/8095/濫用公屋-房屋署-私隱專員公署-8129/查濫用公屋-家屬質疑房署違程序公義-眾新聞揭三大問題</a>"},{"pid":"8132cf5b4f5b965fc169ea686e69f2bac44ac748","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.gangpiaoquan.com/Upload/detail/2017-06-02/5930d40c45b6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gangpiaoquan.com%2FUpload%2Fdetail%2F2017-06-02%2F5930d40c45b6d.jpg&h=44bbf03e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a119bf705c4d5d9ca4b6c97cd4569ea013b5d8b","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:47:53.000Z","msg":"即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740c53ba3b6787b2a4085a5fe0de57bf04b71b1f","tid":495010,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"e5d1b763269fcea5bab6ecb603f54fdcbdf2c931","tid":495010,"uid":93900,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.gangpiaoquan.com/Upload/detail/2017-06-02/5930d40c45b6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gangpiaoquan.com%2FUpload%2Fdetail%2F2017-06-02%2F5930d40c45b6d.jpg&h=44bbf03e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n房署趕佢走既原因係 租戶逾三個月非經常持續居於單位<br />\n富戶政策先豁免廢老,無話其他situation都豁免廢老喎 <br />\n文盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810c7828c2e34faee7ed23e6973b9d8ddaddd3fe","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"最後肯定轉交社署跟進，跟住又特快公屋上樓，根本混吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de071ca3ed2fa52f4e84266b21d7ba0daffc3f8d","tid":495010,"uid":33572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"廢老加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd1f619d19c6f25688af7861cd7bb8677818387","tid":495010,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.gangpiaoquan.com/Upload/detail/2017-06-02/5930d40c45b6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gangpiaoquan.com%2FUpload%2Fdetail%2F2017-06-02%2F5930d40c45b6d.jpg&h=44bbf03e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個淨係for富戶<br />\n佢長時間唔係公屋住咪照趕"},{"pid":"f4a570b6737c057600b3052bb11e34be1205f0d5","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"個調查好誇張，用咁多人力物力招呼一個廢老，不如call埋FBI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63e8bda64406f23026b7b6dcbe9810d1ecf2c04","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"社署一跟進，成個調查根本KO，跟住又有新公屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a02d29664d12930c9b7871d95cf24de1a62f77d","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:56:57.000Z","msg":"瞓床位，又唔見有政府人上來做下家訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f75688b57af4958d83faa0da511ae2dfdfd1ba","tid":495010,"uid":96375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"而家係生人霸死地<br />\n你入左護老院幾年 丟空間公屋<br />\n房署收番有咩問題"},{"pid":"4b8fa951c5c2bf99f3d56203cbad8c52721272c7","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢老尋求禮義廉議員協助、社署、關愛組織、媒體輿論....即加10000000分"},{"pid":"e3c1d2b078f41e85bebf2aa299049e464562be1d","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家係生人霸死地<br />\n你入左護老院幾年 丟空間公屋<br />\n房署收番有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢老座咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc9ab6a8c30235a95171c50068c1c4254a7934d","tid":495010,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"廢老唔會有人理架啦，我地只關注metoo"},{"pid":"437f6021ef347f6e0d7e316a8e36895b137a9cf6","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老唔會有人理架啦，我地只關注metoo</blockquote><br />\nmetoo開始out<br />\n<br />\n但廢老座仍屹立不倒.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711300e1d497af1cea50ae982058a5ad09a28a4c","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"劉伯兒子又批評，上訴聆訊場地中環和記大廈（上圖），並沒有無障礙設施，坐輪椅的劉伯出入甚為不便。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8197037128a873c3f176f34cc209173e637f6e","tid":495010,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瞓床位，又唔見有政府人上來做下家訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老貓，我想同你做個家訪"},{"pid":"b08f53dd493bbb31c3556962b133f8814026a949","tid":495010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>瞓床位